- File Naming Notes:
Cmd = Command
Lst = Listener


- Chat message / command feedback colors:
green (§a) 	/ gold (§6): success message
yellow (§e) / gold (§6): info message
red (§c) 	/ gold (§6): fail message


- Exception handling:
Commands:
    1 try catch block
        error feedback
        return false


- Data structure for the plugin.yml:
commands:
   [command1]:
      aliases:
      - [c1]
      permission: teleios.[segment1].[command1]
      description: [description1]
      usage: /[command1]

permissions:
   teleios.[segment1].[command1]:
      description: Allows the [command] command.
      default: true
   teleios.[segment1].[command2]Read:
      description: Allows the [command] command.
      default: true
   teleios.[segment1].[command2]:
      description: Allows the [command] command.
      default: op
